</ol>
<p>That sums up our restaurant marketing guide. Hopefully you can put these restaurant marketing tips to good use! And don&#8217;t forget to read our guide to creating a <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/restaurant-business-plan/">restaurant business plan</a>.</p>
