<p><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/erichuhn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Eric Huhn</a> is the owner and founder of <a href="https://www.kineticsequence.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kinetic Sequence</a>, a digital marketing agency located in Milwaukee, WI. Eric helps law firms grow their practices through all forms of digital marketing. ¬†Eric holds an MBA in marketing which he only regrets when he sees his student loan bill.</p>
